*assignment* Visual Prompt Studio 1.2 Album Cover
*assignment* Studio1.2.md
*prompt* Create a synthesis retro album cover of a yellow Camaro driving on the road with a sunset and ocean behind it. Use lighter and warm lighting from the hood to the trunk of the car, while using deeper shadows on the side of the car facing the audience. Also create an illusion of space with faint small buildings in the background to add a passage of time. Also make the city look a bit more futuristic while the road was driving on seem more rural, the main variety of colors will be yellow, purple, and blue in the album cover. The main focal point is the car, and the main idea is urbanization and how much we change the world in architecture advancements
*assignment* Studio 1.2 PNG
*assignment* Reflection_studio1.2.jpg
